data.description:
This newly built (2021) home features a spacious open-concept floor plan, with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, situated on a generous half-acre lot. The interior boasts modern finishes, large windows that flood the living spaces with natural light, and a seamless flow between the kitchen, dining area, and living room. The master bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom, while two additional bedrooms share a well-appointed second bathroom. The property offers ample outdoor space for landscaping and recreation, making it an ideal blend of contemporary living and natural surroundings. 
Don’t miss your opportunity for this adorable home.
